TEXT.S: P'anoh 48 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 155 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 95% niqan 147 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 5% niqan 8 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Tayal 83%, Saysiyat 8%, Amis 1%, Paiwan 1%, Bunun 1%, Seejiq/Seediq/Seejiq/Seejiq/Sediq 1%, ni rahuq na o 1%.
